                </p>
                <p><i class="z-icon-check-square-o icon-margin"/>Drag &amp; drop attributes of JPA managed classes on
                    widgets or on the property editor to bind them instantly
                </p>
                <p><i class="z-icon-check-square-o icon-margin"/>Edit zul manually in ZUL tab with auto-complete support
